      "created_at": "2024-08-17T22:31:49.575Z",
      "cooked": "<p>This may just be an issue with my trainer only as it has some other gremlins that prevent firmware updates, but am using a Saris H3 and when trying a HR workout when the workout asks for the mode to change from HR+ to ERG the trainer is no longer able to be controlled.  It \u201cgets stuck\u201d and no matter if I\u2019m in ERG, RES, or HR it does not respond and stays at the same difficulty.</p>\n<p>I had wanted to set up a workout as ERG for warm up, change to HR+, and then back to ERG for the cooldown.  It worked fine until the attempted cool down and it would not get easier no matter what I did.</p>\n<p>Work out plan:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/4194c1425433265af5c8e41a9f0ceed322ac294d.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"9m9JYpqFlhflmlDvzWjtVhFFPaJ\" width=\"293\" height=\"118\"></p>\n<p>I was not performing well today so after 55 minutes I hit the skip interval button to go directly from HR+ to ERG and the trainer ran into the problem described above.</p>\n<p>Activity record:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256_2_690x231.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"pHCpfb6M0vR2SxLR5JcR7RpwIaa\" width=\"690\" height=\"231\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256_2_690x231.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/b/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256_2_1035x346.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b4249f42241dd7a6d7230440e782c4321f074256.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"DDE4F5\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1218\u00d7408 58.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I\u2019m going back to ERG only workouts.</p>\n<p>Regards<br>\nDave</p>",
